post.description:
Sample request with session naming convention:
            
    POST api/contents/createcontent
    {
       "Description": "USA_Arizona_Phoenix_123",
       "ContentNameParts": 
        [
            {
                "Order": 0,
                "Question": "Country",
                "Answer": "USA"
            },
            {
                "Order": 1,
                "Question": "State",
                "Answer": "Arizona"
            },
            {
                "Order": 2,
                "Question": "City",
                "Answer": "Phoenix"
            },
            {
                "Order": 3,
                "Question": "SomeId",
                "Answer": 123
            }
        ]
    }
    
Sample request without session naming convention:
            
    POST api/contents/createcontent
    {
       "Description": null (or any string value)
    }
    
Sample response:
            
    {
       "ontentId": 123
    }

Sample request (simple form with 3 questions):

    {
        "Name": "Metal form",
        "Controls": [
                        {
                            "ControlType": 1 (Text),
                            "Label": "Type the name of your favourite band",
                            "Order": 0
                        },
                        
                        {
                            "ControlType": 3 (Checkboxlist),
                            "Label": "Select the bands you prefer most",
                            "Order": 1,
                            "Options": [
                                            {
                                                "Value": "Metallica",
                                                "Order": 0
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "Value": "Manowar",
                                                "Order": 1
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "Value": "Tool",
                                                "Order": 2
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "Value": "Rammstein",
                                                "Order": 3
                                            }
                                       ]
                        },
                        
                        {
                            "ControlType": 4 (Radiobuttonlist),
                            "Label": "Have you ever attended your favourite band show?",
                            "Order": 2,
                            "Options": [
                                            {
                                                "Value": "Yes",
                                                "Order": 0
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "Value": "No",
                                                "Order": 1
                                            }
                                       ]
                        }
                    ]
    }

Sample response:
            
    {
       "FormId": 123
    }
